title: Lucifer Fawkes
description:
I haven't read these yet, but they look like something some of y'all would definitely be into. Looks like a slightly futuristic, sci-fi, alternative super hero, horror (definitely dark) kind of deal, and the artwork looks great in all of them.

--------------------------------------------------------
Created by Brian Meredith. Books are all one-shots, but they go in this order...

Lucifer Fawkes: Orcus Ex Machina
Rorschach Entertainment, 2004, 34 pages
Written by Ulf Imwiehe 
Illustrated by Jim Keplinger

Lucifer Fawkes: Bloodflow
Rorschach Entertainment, 2004, 34 pages
Written by C William Russette 
Illustrated by Ryan Seargent

Lucifer Fawkes: The Blind Ones
Rorschach Entertainment, 2004, 34 pages
Written by C William Russette, Brian Meredith
Penciled by Augie Pagan
Inked by James Taylor, James Dean Smith
